<br>
Yakut packed her traveling gear which included her shaman rug, candles, pentacle disk, wand, athame, candle snuffer, staff and a travel size cauldron. After finishing up her preparations, the Amazon dried her hair, braided it and then placed her Dragon mask over her face.<br>
<br>
The Tanais Valley Queen, unlike others, wore her mask only in ceremonies or when going outside the Amazon Nation. From there, Yakut walked out into the Royal's housing area, and turned right towards Shy's cabin which was sitting next to the path that lead past Raven's Army housing and towards the center of the City.<br>
<br>
